, no ramming of national tradition down throat.\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3564, \"end\": 3569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.294398393033129e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3605, \"end\": 3611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999767196643, \"rank\": 2.3276695569876917e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No city\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"no overdoing\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3661}, {\"ngram\": \"the pageantry\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3675}, {\"ngram\": \"no ramming\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"national tradition\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"throat\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was patriotism and pride, sure, but also a distinct lack of exceptionalism, right from the moment the world's most famous international sports stars were invited to play roles in the opening ceremony that are usually reserved for the homegrown.\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"patriotism\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3746}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"a distinct lack\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3788}, {\"ngram\": \"exceptionalism\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3806}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3829}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's most famous international sports stars\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3880}, {\"ngram\": \"roles\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3907}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3931}, {\"ngram\": \"the homegrown\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What the Olympics might consist of in four Games' time is anyone's guess,with new sports to be trialled in LA(cricket and flag football) and staples such as boxing and equestrian under threat.\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"four Games' time\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4032}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone's guess\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4050}, {\"ngram\": \"new sports\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4066}, {\"ngram\": \"LA(cricket\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4095}, {\"ngram\": \"flag football\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"staples\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4126}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4141}, {\"ngram\": \"threat\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You would hope that by 2040 stadium DJs might have a repertoire expanded beyond Sweet Caroline and Freed from Desire, as well.\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4251, \"end\": 4265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweet_Caroline\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.19697810261089e-31, \"text\": \"Sweet Caroline\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweet_Caroline\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweet_Caroline\"}, {\"begin\": 4281, \"end\": 4287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7515576868833565e-40, \"text\": \"Desire\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Desire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2040 stadium DJs\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"a repertoire\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"Freed\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speculating on specifics though, feels an act of folly, when so much of the big picture is in flux.\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"specifics\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"an act\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"folly\", \"from\": 4348, \"to\": 4353}, {\"ngram\": \"the big picture\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"flux\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And what will Britain look like by 2040, given at one stage during these Olympics, it appeared Team GB's athletes would be returning home to an island aflame?\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4413, \"end\": 4420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999979209372908, \"rank\": 2.0554154329257036e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 4494, \"end\": 4501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.8422371577505898, \"rank\": 0.18730878550985178, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one stage\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4480}, {\"ngram\": \"an island aflame\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then again, France, too, was \\u00ada fractious place only weeks before their own, very different torch was lit.\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4571, \"end\": 4577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9233158428989224, \"rank\": 0.08301175392256512, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00ada fractious place\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4606}, {\"ngram\": \"their own, very different torch\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is naive to think the sense of healing and harmony that has infected the city this past few weeks will last, but also impossible not to leave Paris lifted by the knowledge that it happened and it was real.\", \"from\": 4667, \"to\": 4875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4812, \"end\": 4817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.294398393033129e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sense\", \"from\": 4688, \"to\": 4697}, {\"ngram\": \"healing\", \"from\": 4701, \"to\": 4708}, {\"ngram\": \"harmony\", \"from\": 4713, \"to\": 4720}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4747}, {\"ngram\": \"the knowledge\", \"from\": 4828, \"to\": 4841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On that basis alone, the Games cannot come back to Britain soon enough.\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4927, \"end\": 4934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999979209372908, \"rank\": 2.0554154329257036e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that basis\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4897, \"to\": 4906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyl